# Movie Search App

A responsive movie search application built with JavaScript, HTML, and CSS.

## Features

* Search movies by title
* Fetch movie data from an external API
* Display detailed movie information
* Filter movies by genre
* Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop
* Loading progress bar while fetching data
* Dynamic movie cards with movie details

## Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (ES6+)
* Fetch API
* Async/Await

## What I Practiced

* Working with APIs
* Fetching and displaying data
* Asynchronous JavaScript (Async/Await)
* DOM Manipulation
* Array Methods (map, filter, split)
* Responsive Web Design
* Git & GitHub

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository
2. Open the project folder
3. Run the project using a local server By adding Api
4.get Api key from https://www.omdbapi.com/


